Dear emergency1
I see that ur question has been answered by candanga. There are a few progs on this site itself which can create .iso files very easily. In order of preference, they are 1. Alcohol 120%. 2. Clone CD or Clone DVD 3. Ultra ISO (I use this one), 4. Daemon tools (free software) and of course a host of others. Experiment a bit with these and you would be a master in making ISOs out of CDs or DVDs. All the best and happy seeding.
